{"tid":1262861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又燈］蕭若元指林鄭向中央辭職　特首辦澄清：絕無此事！","createTime":"2019-06-28T01:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T02:03:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55f39485d9b60d552387d9c0e99fef26973600aa","tid":1262861,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:47:24.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂引發林鄭政府的管治危機，時事評論員蕭若元今天指出，有小道消息，指特首林鄭月娥已經遞辭職信。對於這個傳言，特首辦公室回應說︰「無此事！」<br />\n　　　　<br />\n事實上，林鄭近日不公開露面，只是想維持低調，以免再惹火頭，本月22日，林鄭還與全體問責司局長，一齊在禮賓府，開了5個小時集思會，度橋如何重建市民信心，未來三年施政怎樣更貼近民心。換言之，林鄭是完全沒有要辭職的跡象。<br />\n<br />\n至於北京，立場仍是撐林鄭，中方官員近日與親中陣營見面，都是希望他們支持林鄭。有親中人士指，北京肯定不想林鄭下台，因為這只會令香港形勢更加混亂，傳林鄭辭職，是不安好心。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2386989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2386989&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=e86031ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2386989</a><br />\n<br />\n燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81ac2a178d30b4203fb68b99919e421b02e6ce3","tid":1262861,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:01:14.000Z","msg":"燒山奶共"},{"pid":"3de5220fe06ae5deda9a804a754415215d34e27c","tid":1262861,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:01:37.000Z","msg":"派錢都可以派到天怒人怨，都唔知仲有咩做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0181feb9e193a81649d1aa7a5b5f54c3a23f779","tid":1262861,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de5220fe06ae5deda9a804a754415215d34e27c","tid":1262861,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy